		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="education-container">
		<div class="education-item">
			<img src="/static/image/ncnu.jpg" alt="大學" class="school-image">
		</div>
		<div class="school-info">
			<h3 class="school-name">暨南大學</h3>
			<p>暨南在埔里，埔里景點日月潭，日月潭變成我現在的家。</p>
		</div>
